Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:27.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改革者…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:29.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道得很清楚嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:34.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.11,0:11:35.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎
