Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.61,0:11:46.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距到達目標還有543秒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.83,0:11:50.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  特瑞亞  洛克恩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.37,0:11:59.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現敵艦！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.88,0:12:02.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正沿著赤道環駛向這邊
