Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.43,0:12:08.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎擊艦隊開始炮擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.53,0:12:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他們推到Memento Mori的射擊軌道上去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.05,0:12:16.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題！
