Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.49,0:12:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始共振
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.64,0:13:06.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密進入敵人衛星兵器的射擊軌道了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐
