Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.09,0:13:18.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.05,0:13:20.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.34,0:13:27.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Memento Mori開始掃射！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.55,0:13:30.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.32,0:13:31.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里路亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.66,0:13:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了
